{"tid":1991697,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"重開內地口岸惹關注　袁國勇：至少要14天無不明本地個案","createTime":"2020-04-27T15:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T15:16:04.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"47b4275607a972627fb6d7727136dc905016c9fc","tid":1991697,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T15:09:58.000Z","msg":"政府對內地來港人士實施的強制檢疫令將於5月7日屆滿，而香港對上一宗源頭不明的本地感染個案於上周日(19日)錄得，社會關注政府會否重開來往內地的口岸。香港大學微生物學系講座教授袁國勇認為，香港能否重開連接內地的口岸，至少要14至28天沒有源頭不明的本地確診個案，又指即使重開口岸，亦必須確保由內地入境的人士，於入境前7日及入境時接受病毒測試並呈陰性反應，以及要繼續進行健康申報。<br />\n<br />\n袁又指出，現在所看到的情況全為14天前做的「工夫」，因此就算現在沒有確診個案，亦應先觀察一會。<br />\n<br />\n對於香港於8日內4次錄得零確診，是否代表疫情受控，袁指，香港無法獨自運作，因此當其他國家仍有疫情，都不能說香港疫情受控。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200427/bkn-20200427200647251-0427_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200427%2Fbkn-20200427200647251-0427_00822_001.html&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4W2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=a44a6785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200427/bkn-20200427200647251-0427_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">袁生，好耐無見喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"880ee73a69bd28daee447fc7b56abd5289a54260","tid":1991697,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T15:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1kJ7Ufw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1kJ7Ufw.gif&h=ee5bd90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新登記選民截止日期：2020年5月2日<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4W2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=0963ed25\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jL0uupX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjL0uupX.gif&h=b8ede5bd&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}